  "description": "A pack that focuses on exploration, environment/graphical enhancements, gameplay variety; with multiplayer interactions kept in mind",
  "body": "### Summary\nA pack that focuses on exploration, environment/graphical enhancements, gameplay variety; with multiplayer interactions kept in mind. Many new mobs, dimensions, biomes, structures, utilities and events have been added to keep things interesting. Create and Computercraft have been added to provide some interesting side mechanical mechanics. Comes with Complementary Shaders V4 with a custom config. Many multiplayer focused mods such as Xaeor's World Map, Open Parties & Claims, Voice Chat, Emotes and many text chat enhancements.\n\nThe world generation has been greatly improved thanks to Terralith, Oh The Biomes You'll Go, many cave enhancement mods and the Continents mod that breaks the world up into land masses ranging from island archipelagos to massive continents separated by ocean. In the newly generated oceans much more varied aquatic life can be found. On land you'll find new mobs, bosses, plants and enemies.  Traverse the world with the new airplanes, hookshots, balloons, Waystones or ships.\n\nThe day/night cycle has been changed to a 10 minute night and a 45 minute day can be edited in the config folder time-and-wind -> time-date.json. \n\n### Public Server\nIf you would like to join a dedicated 24/7 server running this pack or if you have any issues/suggestions message me directly on discord @kozmikk\n\n## Coming Soon\nFixed aquatic life spawning with Hybrid Aquatic Update, wakes mod, custom shader settings and more improvements\n\n### Coming Later\n- Server Files; should work on a server by itself but later I will provide dedicated server-only files\n\n### Complete Mod List\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/additional-structures\">Additional Structures</a>\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/adventurez\">AdventureZ</a>\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/alternate-current\">Alternative Current</a>\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/angling\">Angling</a>\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/appleskin\